* &quot;Listening to Brahms&quot; (1988)
* &quot;Boobs&quot; (1989) Winner of the 1990 Hugo Award for the best short story
* &quot;Beauty and the Opera or the Phantom Beast&quot; (1996)
* &quot;Peregrines&quot; (2004)

===Play===
